name: Cathy Kirkland
message: Dear Mr. Crixdord, I am & Joupl Dowl Qmten, and have been for twenty years. But I am close to moving to Orlando. In turn, have got five months and six weeks to send double letters for the good state and role. This past Christmas, three family members got our dreams. With the coupon in their hands, got three dollars in coupons and cards. Then they got a candy. Got Mr. Clienkn. I did not get one. 51751 7062. Remember what did the day.
